@node installation "Installation"

 Bview is at the moment only one program so you can copy it from
 the release directory/disk to your Harddisk etc...

 To install the libraries there is Bview.xicon press it and the libraries
 reqtools.library 38.x 
 will be installed in your LIBS
 directory.

 See that your @{ " requirements " link requirements } are ok...

@endnode

